Deputy President William Ruto on Sunday, December 22, 2019, responded for the first time since Machakos Governor Alfred Mutua accused him of threatening his life. “Yule jamaa mwingine mliskia alilalamika juzi, ati nilimsalimia…ati nilifanya nini…(laughs)…ati nilimsalimia tu nikamwangalia, akakimbia kunishtaki kwa polisi”